                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-929-18510407 t18510407-929-punishment-103"></join>Transported for Seven Years</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>(<hi rend="italic">There was another indictment against the prisoner.</hi>)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before the Third Jury.</hi>
